    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4597424/" class="title-link">呼唤那远去的背影</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4597424"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jwa/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1355332-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jwa/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">云起半山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-24"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-24 20:39:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4597424_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  之前我看过几本介绍民国时期的文人的书，诸如《笔杆子》、《民国韵事》等，只简单地用素描的勾勒、散文的笔法，从侧面某一视角，单个的让读者了解那些名人的逸事趣事。如今看到《南渡北归》以后，再度见到了那些熟悉的名字，顿时感到了强大的兴趣和吸引力，读后更是被大师们的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4597424/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">21有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4597424_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4597424_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4624557">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4624557/" class="title-link">知识分子的命运——评《北归》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4624557"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yebuguoruci/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3319508-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yebuguoruci/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">庞二哥</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-13 20:44:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4624557_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  刚刚合上岳南先生的大著《南渡北归》的第二部《北归》，就上来写这篇书评了。 	《南渡北归》可以说是煌煌巨著，一共有三部，分别为《南渡》、《北归》和《离别》。目前我看到了其中的两部，每一部都是洋洋五十多万字，我想一套书下来至少要有一百五六十万字。厚重的书，写的是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4624557/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">23有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4624557_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4624557_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4624734">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4624734/" class="title-link">三流文笔四流编校</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4624734"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1182787-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">拔刀诀</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-13 22:11:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4624734_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一流人物，二流内容，三流文笔，四流编校。 书中引述资料部分颇有可观之处，大体上能对那一代学人大师整体状况有所了解。作者叙述部分则不堪，言辞粗鄙，行文轻浮，几欲令人拍案摔书。 此书编校质量亦差，书中错字、别字、漏字随处可见。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4624734/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4624734_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4624734_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










